## Cognitive and Personality Correlates  

| Trait/Factor                      | Description                                                                                   | Impact on Conspiracy Belief                              | Source                                                                                           |
|---------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Need for Cognitive Closure       | Desire for definite answers and aversion to ambiguity                                        | Increases susceptibility to conspiracies                 | Marchlewska et al., 2018                                                                        |
| Hypersensitive Agency Detection | Overattribution of events to intentional agents                                              | Leads to seeing conspiracies where none exist             | Douglas et al., 2016                                                                             |
| Intellectual Humility            | Openness to new ideas and acknowledgment of one's cognitive limitations                      | Lower levels associated with conspiracy belief            | Jarrett, 2022                                                                                   |
| Paranoia                        | Suspiciousness and belief in personal persecution                                            | Heightens conspiracy endorsement                           | Swan, 2020                                                                                      |
| Analytical Thinking             | Ability to critically evaluate information                                                   | Lower levels linked to higher conspiracy belief           | Pierre, 2019                                                                                   |
| Need for Uniqueness             | Desire to feel special and different                                                        | Motivates belief in multiple or contradictory conspiracies| Lantian et al., 2017                                                                            |

